//만들어진 RDD를 실행해봐서 테스트를한번 해보자
val head = carRDD.take(10)

//foreach와 println을 함게 사용하여 배열의 각 값을 줄 단위로 출력하는 방법도 있음
head.foreach(println)

//김재형

//아래의 코드는 apache.spark.sql.types이하의 ._ 즉, 모든것
//DoubleType, StringType, StructField, StructType  <<--이것들이다
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._

//컬럼 지정~! 
val carColumns = Array(
        
        new StructField("Year",IntegerType,true),
        new StructField("Time",IntegerType,true),
        new StructField("Minute",IntegerType,true),
        new StructField("D/N",StringType,true),
        new StructField("Day",StringType,true),
        
        new StructField("Dead",IntegerType,true),
        new StructField("casualties",IntegerType,true),
        new StructField("heavy",IntegerType,true),
        new StructField("light",IntegerType,true),
        new StructField("Caller",IntegerType,true),
        
        new StructField("SIDO",StringType,true),
        new StructField("KUNKU",StringType,true),
        new StructField("Type",StringType,true),
        

        new StructField("NULL1",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL2",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL3",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL4",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL5",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL6",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL7",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL8",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL9",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL10",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL11",StringType,true),
        new StructField("NULL12",StringType,true),
        
        
        new StructField("Longitude",FloatType,true),
        new StructField("Latitude",FloatType,true)
        
    )

//스키마생성
val carSchema = new StructType(carColumns)
    
//데이터패쓰 지정
val DataPath = "/CarAccident/Data/"
//데이터에 만들어준 스키마를 적용하여 데이터 프레임 생성
val carDF = spark.read.schema(carSchema).csv(DataPath)
